Currency System of Aetheria
The standard currency used across most human kingdoms (and accepted in many other realms) is based on four metals. The exchange rate is 1:100 between each tier.

Currency Units
Copper,1 Copper,Copper Piece (CP),Very common
Silver,100 Copper,Silver Piece (SP),Standard day-to-day coin
Gold,"100 Silver (10,000 CP)",Gold Piece (GP),High value
Platinum,"100 Gold (1,000,000 CP)",Platinum Piece (PP),Extremely rare & valuable

Everyday Value Reference

1 Copper (CP) ≈ Price of one decent loaf of bread or a tankard of basic ale.
5–10 Copper ≈ A simple meal (stew + bread) at a roadside tavern.
1 Silver (SP) ≈ A day’s wages for an unskilled laborer or a night in a cheap inn.
5–15 Silver ≈ A good set of traveling clothes or a month’s rent in a small room.
50–200 Silver ≈ A well-made sword or leather armor.
2–5 Gold ≈ A small house.

